Immediate goals

* For loops on Hashes.
* Nested Variable queries.

Short term goals

* Optimize the parser a lot more.
* call, default statements.
* insert, include, process, and wrapper statements.
* block statements.
* given/when statements.

Medium term goals

* Whitespace control.
* Precompiled/cached templates.
* Tag Styles (definable start_tag, end_tag, etc.)
  - Interpolate can go to hell.
* Capture of directive output.
* Multiple directive blocks.
* Filters.

Long term goals

* Directive comments.
* Side-effect notation.

